{"tid":58125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭賣豬仔來港工作覆核勝訴　巴漢斥警：若仔細調查投訴，案件不需拖延至今","createTime":"2016-12-28T14:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T16:07:56.000Z","uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"929ec1769ab315edc22161caca532f9544033362","tid":58125,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161228/s00001/1482916247078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161228%2Fs00001%2F1482916247078&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fX8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=c6d852dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161228%2Fs00001%2F1482916247078&h=974e4bd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161228/s00001/1482916247078</a><br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦籍男子稱早年被販賣來港工作，卻不獲發薪金，更遭僱主毆打，4年後被送返國。他之後偷渡來港，以販賣人口受害人身分向多個政府部門求助，但不獲理會，遂在早前提出司法覆核。高院上星期裁定政府未有履行《人權法》訂明的責任，導致申請人未受保護。<br />\n<br />\n以ZN為代號的申請人今接受訪問時直言，對裁決結果感高興，又多次感謝其律師協助，令公義得已彰顯。ZN表示，當初他多次向入境處和警方求助，但兩個部門互相卸責，他甚至每次求助前都會祈禱希望獲受理，惟最終仍不獲理會。 <br />\n<br />\nZN偷渡來港後，<span style=\"color: red;\">2012年流落街頭時認識為香港人的現任妻子，兩人其後誕下一女兒</span>，ZN現時以受養人身份申請簽證留港工作，養活一家。<br />\n<br />\n被問到會否向政府索償，ZN激動地反問，政府是否可以補償失去的時間？政府能否彌補他所受的痛苦？說畢ZN不禁落淚，又批評若警方可仔細調查他的投訴，案件不需拖延到今天。<br />\n<br />\nZN在港興訟，但他遠在巴基斯坦的家人卻一直受到其前僱主威嚇，其母更一度以為他已被殺害，擔心過度需入院。ZN直言現時最希望是能回到巴基斯坦，讓母親看看自己的女兒，再親口向母親道歉，感謝她多年來因事件需承受如此多苦楚，但是ZN深知其前僱主不會輕易放過自己，回家只是一個未完的夢。<br />\n<br />\n學下人啦，流落街頭都溝到女啊死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d046b861b74e0ccd5364c2fdd4796a3494e7786b","tid":58125,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533e8bd713260fb7c185ac0a27616f33fa38b208","tid":58125,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n望咩啊柒頭"},{"pid":"a818dac6b3f1a2e905bb2211c19926676f9aef31","tid":58125,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"真心講<br />\nd老細勁仆街, 唔出糧再講人走"},{"pid":"0f6a3c048f0da3052e8c277740e2d408421869c3","tid":58125,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"就咁睇巴基果邊都幾恐怖下<br />\n唔怪得班大陸仔咁憎巴基<br />\n因為巴基捱過苦完全唔怕大陸仔"},{"pid":"88458438335ecb9c2cb0eac501d61d788e5175fd","tid":58125,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:22:01.000Z","msg":"港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90695ad4876af5d5e20a43f0709e36f25b353cf","tid":58125,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n南亞佬屌閪大大力，條港女先識食啊"},{"pid":"4eeef590b92390ca2018fc561d2e413b9b65a1c1","tid":58125,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁睇巴基果邊都幾恐怖下<br />\n唔怪得班大陸仔咁憎巴基<br />\n因為巴基捱過苦完全唔怕大陸仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸仔有咩國家人係唔憎？"}]}